<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Introduction
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            FutKui is a sports team communication app designed to help teams,
            clubs, and sports organizations stay connected. We are committed to
            protecting your privacy and ensuring your team's communications
            remain secure and private.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Information We Collect
          </h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
            Account Information
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Email address (for magic code authentication)</li>
            <li>Display name and profile handle</li>
            <li>Profile creation timestamp</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
            Team and Group Data
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Sports club names and descriptions</li>
            <li>Group avatars and customization settings</li>
            <li>Team membership information</li>
            <li>Group admin roles and permissions</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
            Messages and Media
          </h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Text messages sent within team chats</li>
            <li>Images and media files shared in groups</li>
            <li>Message reactions and emoji responses</li>
            <li>Message timestamps and delivery status</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            How We Use Your Information
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>
              <strong>Team Communication:</strong> Enable real-time messaging
              between team members
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Group Management:</strong> Allow creation and management
              of sports clubs and teams
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Media Sharing:</strong> Facilitate sharing of photos from
              games, training sessions, and team events
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Authentication:</strong> Verify user identity through
              magic code authentication
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>App Functionality:</strong> Provide core features like
              message reactions, member lists, and group invites
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Data Storage and Security
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            FutKui uses InstantDB for secure, real-time data synchronization.
            Your data is stored with industry-standard security measures:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Secure file storage for images and media</li>
            <li>Permission-based access control for all team data</li>
            <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Data Sharing and Disclosure
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third
            parties. Your team communications remain private within your sports
            club. We may only disclose information when:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Required by law or legal process</li>
            <li>Necessary to protect user safety or prevent harm</li>
            <li>With your explicit consent</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Your Rights and Controls
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>
              <strong>Access:</strong> View and download your personal data
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Correction:</strong> Update your profile information and
              display name
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request removal of your account and
              associated data
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Group Control:</strong> Leave teams, remove messages, or
              delete groups you admin
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Privacy Settings:</strong> Control who can add you to
              groups and see your profile
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Team Admin Responsibilities
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Sports club admins have additional responsibilities for their team's
            data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Ensuring appropriate use of the platform by team members</li>
            <li>Managing group membership and permissions</li>
            <li>Respecting team members' privacy preferences</li>
            <li>
              Following applicable sports organization guidelines and policies
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Children's Privacy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            FutKui is designed for sports teams of all ages. For users under 13,
            we require parental consent and provide additional privacy
            protections. Team admins and coaches are responsible for ensuring
            appropriate supervision and privacy practices for youth sports
            teams.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Data Retention
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as
            needed to provide services. When you delete your account or leave
            all teams:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700">
            <li>Your messages and media are removed from active systems</li>
            <li>Profile information is deleted within 30 days</li>
            <li>Backup systems are purged within 90 days</li>
            <li>
              Anonymous usage analytics may be retained for service improvement
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Updates to This Policy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            We may update this privacy policy to reflect changes in our
            practices or applicable laws. Significant changes will be announced
            through the app or via email. Your continued use of FutKui after
            updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
